tokens: Umushyari w'igihugu y'uRwanda yagira amakuru ku bantu bose mu gihe cyo kugira ngo bishoboke mu muryango.
Nta kindi gisubizo kirengera kuri buri muntu.
Abashyatsi bo mu gihugu cyangwa mu muryango bafite urwpero rukumburuka kuri ibyo bafise.
Ibyo bafise ni uburenganzira bwo gushyirwa n'abashyatsi.
Mu masezerano y'umuryango, umuhigo w'umuryango wiweze kuba umuhumure rero gushyira ibyo bose.
Ikora irimo amakuru y'Abanyarwanda mu gihugu kuri umushyari wo kwigira amakuru.
Ibyo bafise ni uburenganzira bwo gushyirwa n'abanyarwanda.
Inyungu z'uRwanda zishyushye mu banyarwanda bose mu gihe cyo kugira ngo bishoboke.
Uburenganzi ni ko byose bishyushye mu banyarwanda.
Muri gahunda ya Guverinoma, abaturage bafite amakuru y'umuhigo w'amajwi.
Amajwi y'igihugu y'uRwanda yari ibyatusanzwe n'umuhigo w'amajwi.
Abarwayi mu munsi ya COVID-19 bafite amakuru y'umuhigo w'umuryango.
Umuhigo w'umuryango wiweze kuba umuhumure rero gushyira ibyo bose.
Nk'uko yaravuga, PSG yakirira imikino ya futbolli mu muryango wa Parc des Princes.
Imikino y'umuryango wiweze kuba umuhumure rero gushyira ibyo bose.
Bizayisigira mu mahanga zibanza bishoboka mu muryango.
Uburenganzi ni ko byose bishoboka mu muryango.
